nk into the ultimate tool of destruction!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 automated defenses to choose from, including the <strong>Tesla Tower!</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 unique maps of <strong>Switzerland</strong>.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Endless</strong> mode to push your PC to the limits!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210620/extras/abd8007ef6ccdf204ec5d0d9444c429c.poster.avif?t=1749865275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210620/extras/abd8007ef6ccdf204ec5d0d9444c429c.webm?t=1749865275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210620/extras/abd8007ef6ccdf204ec5d0d9444c429c.mp4?t=1749865275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210620/extras/74d475dd50f423d6e2e92e3be26a8e38.poster.avif?t=1749865275\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210620/extras/74d475dd50f423d6e2e92e3be26a8e38.webm?t=1749865275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210620/extras/74d475dd50f423d6e2e92e3be26a8e38.mp4?t=1749865275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
